  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598252514426-2AO5UQ6HYEMVXR8LBWPW/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>So excited to use a quote this week that actually 2 of you suggested in the comments of <a href=\"http://www.amytangerine.com/blog/2015/1/9/motivational-monday.html\">this post</a>. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1598252530623-L6KC6L6ZPZBLS2NL6K9M/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Thanks so much Stacie D. and Amy C.! </p><p>Hope to continue spreading more motivation for each of your Mondays this year using <a href=\"http://www.michaels.com/artists-loft-fundamentals-watercolor-pan-set/10122060.html#q=watercolor&amp;start=2\">this watercolor set from Michaels</a> and brush that says Royal 2 on it (can’t remember where it’s from, sorry!). I also found some alternative watercolor options – <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=33086&amp;m=7429&amp;afftrack=watercolor&amp;urllink=store%2Escrapbook%2Ecom%2Fac%2D366901%2Ehtml\">Colortopia Watercolor Set</a> | <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00114RIIQ/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;amp;camp=1789&amp;amp;creative=390957&amp;amp;creativeASIN=B00114RIIQ&amp;amp;linkCode=as2&amp;amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;amp;linkId=SEL4W2XO57Q&amp;lt;a%20href=\">this one</a> | <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B0019IKY58/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;amp;camp=1789&amp;amp;creative=390957&amp;amp;creativeASIN=B0019IKY58&amp;amp;linkCode=as2&amp;amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20&amp;amp;linkId=Y4TM3YCBZ74FFNPO\">and this one.</a> If you have a favorite quote – snarky, silly, or simple in its’ wisdom, please share in the comments!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
